Title: The Midnight Thing
Author: Demo

INT. KITCHEN - NIGHT #1#

JANE leans in the doorway, arms folded. MAX stands at the open fridge, yogurt in hand.

JANE
You said you'd stop doing this.

MAX
(without turning)
Doing what?

JANE
The midnight thing.

MAX freezes.

MAX
This is a snack.

JANE
That's the third "snack" tonight.

MAX
(turning)
You're counting?

JANE
Someone has to.

She crosses to the counter, takes the yogurt, and drops it back in the fridge. The door swings shut.

CUT TO:
